| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3289 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a6c966b9-d09f-5200-b966-4ba446bbfdc9"
